  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together hot sauce, smoky paprika, allspice, garlic, lime juice, and olive oil.",
    "3. Add pork cubes to the marinade and mix well.",
    "4. Thread pork cubes onto skewers.",
    "5. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "6. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until the pork is cooked through.",
    "7. Let skewers rest for 2-3 minutes before serving."
